Station - Class in DataModel.TransportationData.StationData
Class: java.DataModel.TransportationData.StationData.Station
Stores all the information about a specific Station and offers the ability to read, change and compare this information with the information of other stations.
this class implements the Comparator interface in order to be able to sort objects from this class if needed.
Station() - Constructor for class DataModel.TransportationData.StationData.Station
construct an empty station with all the attributes initialized
Station(Station) - Constructor for class DataModel.TransportationData.StationData.Station
constructs a station using the information of another station (creates a copy from the other station)
Stop - Class in DataModel.TransportationData.StopData
Class: java.DataModel.TransportationData.StopData.Stop
Stores all the information about a specific Stop and offers the ability to read, change and compare this information with the information of other Stop.
this class implements the Comparator interface in order to be able to sort objects from this class if needed.
Stop() - Constructor for class DataModel.TransportationData.StopData.Stop

Stop(Stop) - Constructor for class DataModel.TransportationData.StopData.Stop
